{"id": "cpos023", "name": "Cam_Kyuu_702_12_10", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……!\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "... Where is this...? Oh, yeah. I'm at Kyuu Hou Kai. \n... Dreamed about those things again...\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»» Fast Forward»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Still", "Singing"], "content": ""}, {"id": 5, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Store", "Door Opens"], "content": ""}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "...Can't sleep?\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Oh, did I wake you up?\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "I haven't slept yet. I can hear your voice.\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "<i>*shivers*</i>... Yikes, it's so cold... The winter in Node 03 really is freezing.\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "The weather system here hasn't been fully recreated like in Node 08. The differences in temperature are much larger. Do you want me to close the window?\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "It's okay. I wanna look at the night scenery a bit more.\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "At least put on another coat? You don't want to catch a cold. Here.\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "You don't need one?\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "I was just optimizing their equipment in the server room with Nora. It's really damn hot in there. Here, take it.\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Here he is, good guy Simon.\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Yeah, yeah, yeah. Quit your blabbing... \nWere you singing \"Still\" just now? Haven't heard you sing that one for a while.\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "... I was just humming, that's all.\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……\nI've mentioned to my friend in the Administration Bureau about the threats Diego made regarding our families. You don't have to worry about it too much.\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "You mean the Nate you mentioned before? The one who let you escape in the restricted area.\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Yeah.\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "... Why are you telling me this all of a sudden?\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "You said before that when you're feeling distressed, you'll sing that song. So, I made a quick guess.\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "I'm fine... It's just... I remembered some things again.\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "That previous apology... I feel like I was a total mess when I said it. But I still want to say I'm sorry once more. Perhaps I'm still unable to forgive myself, but... can you?\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Didn't I already tell you? You need to let go of the past. If you don't, there's no way you'll ever move forward. Whether or not we can forgive those things is no longer important.\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Yeah... you're right.\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "<i>*Yawn*~</i>\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "So you do yawn? What a rare sight.\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "I haven't slept in two days... I probably should actually sleep. You ought to sleep early as well. Tomorrow, we'll use PAFF's ability to check for some more clues. I'll need you to provide me some information on what happened back then.\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "I want to feel the breeze for a little longer. I'll sleep soon.\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Oh, then I'll leave this coat here.\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Eh? I don't want it. It's got that sweat stink of yours on it. Take it.\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Really? Let me take a whiff... It's not that bad, isn't it?\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Oh, it's QUITE bad. Take it already.\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Hey, there's something inside. Don't throw it... ah!\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Wahh!\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Impact", "Falls down"], "content": ""}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "... Owww...!\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "image", "attrs": ["cpos2301"], "content": ""}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Move", "Stands up"], "content": ""}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "... I'm gonna sleep now, goodnight.\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "... Yeah, goodnight.\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_2", "Footsteps"], "content": ""}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\nI... I forgave you a long time ago. Don't ask that anymore.\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "......\n... Thank you.\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Store", "Door Opens"], "content": ""}, {"id": 51, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Impact", "Crashing"], "content": ""}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "Waah!?\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "NEKO... What are you doing?\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "Eh? Ahahaha... it's... umm... ah! Yes! There's huge news on iM! Things got really, really bad!! Another large-scale terrorist attack has occurred in Node 08! It's very close to uncle JOE's shop! NEKO is here to tell you guys that!\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "WHAT!?\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "What's happening!?\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "ここは……？\nそっか、玖凰會にいるんだった。\nまた夢を……\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»早送り»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Still", "歌声"], "content": ""}, {"id": 5, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Store", "ドアが開く"], "content": ""}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……眠れないのか？\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "あ、起こしちゃった？\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "まだ寝てなかった。\n声が聞こえたから。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "うわ、さむ……\nNode03の冬マジで寒いじゃん。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "こっちの天気システムはまだNode08ほど完璧じゃない。\nだから、寒暖差が激しいんだ。\n窓、閉めろよ。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "いい。\nもっと外の風景眺めてたい。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "なら、上着くらい着ろ。\n風邪ひくぞ。ほら。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "あんたは着なくていいの？\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "俺はさっきまでNoraと機械室にいたから。\n逆に暑くて死にそうだ。これ着ろよ。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "出たよ、お人よしSimon。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "はいはい、そうだな。\n黙って着ろ。\n……さっき歌ってたの、《Still》か？\nお前がこの曲を歌うのは久しぶりだな。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……適当に口ずさんでただけだよ。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………\nDiegoの言ってた家族のことだが、管理局の友人にも伝えておいた。\n心配する必要はない。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "前に言ってたNateって人？\n管制区であんたを見逃した……\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "あぁ。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……なんで急にそんな話？\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "昔言ってただろ。\n何か不安なことがある時にその歌を歌うんだって。\nだからだ。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "あたしは大丈夫だって……\n少し昔のことを思い出しただけだから。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "この前の謝罪……あたし言ってること滅茶苦茶だったよね。\nもう1回謝りたい。\n……それでもあたしはきっと自分が許せない。\nあんたは……あたしを許してくれる？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "言っただろ？\nお前は過去を手放すべきだ。\n手放さない限り、前に進むことはできない。\n俺やお前が許すかどうかなんて重要じゃない。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "うん……そうだね。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "ふわぁあ……\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "あんたがあくびなんて珍しいじゃん。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "2日も寝てないからな……\nそろそろ寝ないとヤバそうだ。\nお前も早く寝ろよ。\n明日はまたPAFFの力を使って手掛かりを探す。\nお前にもらった情報が必要になる。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "うん、もう少し風にあたったら。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "そうか。\nなら、上着は着てろ。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "は？いらないんだけど。\n汗臭いし。持ってってよ。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "嘘だろ？どれ……そんな臭くないだろ。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "臭いっつの。ほら、持ってけ持ってけ。\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "おい、ポケットに物が入ってるんだから投げるな……うわ！\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "うわあっ！\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Impact", "転ぶ"], "content": ""}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……いったぁ……！\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "image", "attrs": ["cpos2301"], "content": ""}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Move", "起き上がる"], "content": ""}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……俺はもう寝る。\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……うん、おやすみ。\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_2", "足音"], "content": ""}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………\n俺はとっくにお前のことを許してるよ。\nもう聞くな。\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "………\n……ありがとう。\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Store", "ドアが開く"], "content": ""}, {"id": 51, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Impact", "ぶつかる"], "content": ""}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "うっわあ！！\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "NEKO……こんなところで何してるんだ。\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "えっ？あはは～……えっと……あ！そう！\nNode08が大変なの！\nまた大規模テロだって！！\nJOEおじじのお店の近くだよ！\nこれを伝えに来たの！\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "なんだって！\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "どうした！？\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……這裡是……？對了，我在玖凰會。\n……又夢到那些事了……\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Still", "歌聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 5, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Store", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……睡不著？\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "啊，吵醒你了嗎？\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "我還沒睡。聲音傳過來了。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "哇，好冷……Node 03 的冬天還真冷啊。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "這邊的天氣系統不像 Node 08 還原得那麼完整，溫差比較大。把窗戶關上吧？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "沒關係，我想再多看一下夜景。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "至少加件外套吧？會感冒的，喏。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "你不穿嗎？\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "我剛剛跟 Nora 在機房優化他們的設備，熱得半死。給妳。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "出現了，爛好人 Simon。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "對啦對啦，少囉唆。\n……剛剛在唱《Still》嗎？好久沒聽妳唱這首歌了。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……隨口亂哼而已。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\nDiego 威脅家人的事情我跟管理局的朋友說了，我想不用太擔心。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "你之前提到的那個 Nate 嗎？在管制區放你走的。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "嗯。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……怎麼突然說這個？\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "妳以前說過，感到不安的時候就會唱那首歌，所以我猜的。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "我沒事啦……只是又稍微想起一些事情。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "之前的道歉……我覺得自己說得亂七八糟的，但是我還是想再說一次對不起。我可能還是無法原諒自己，但是……你能原諒我嗎？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "我說過了吧？妳該放下過去，不放下就無法前進。我或妳有沒有原諒那些事情都不重要了。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "嗯……說得也是。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "哈～～\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "你居然在打哈欠，真稀奇。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "我兩天沒睡了啊……好像真的該去睡一下。妳也早點睡吧，明天會用 PAFF 的能力再調查一些線索，需要妳提供當時給我的情報。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "我想再吹一下風，待會吧。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "喔，那外套就給妳了。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "咦？我才不要，上面都是汗臭味，拿去啦。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "真的假的？我聞……還好吧？\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "明明就有，拿走拿走。\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "喂，裡面有東西，不要用丟……哇！\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "唔哇！\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Impact", "摔倒"], "content": ""}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……好痛……！\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "image", "attrs": ["cpos2301"], "content": ""}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Move", "起身"], "content": ""}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……我去睡了，晚安。\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……嗯，晚安。\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_2", "腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n我……早就原諒妳了，不用再問了。\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……。\n……謝謝你。\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Store", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 51, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Impact", "碰撞"], "content": ""}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "哇！？\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "NEKO……妳在幹嘛？\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "咦？啊哈哈……就……那個，啊！對了！iM 上有大新聞啊！不得了了！Node 08 又出現大規模的恐怖攻擊了！在 JOE 叔叔的店附近啊！NEKO 是要來跟你們說這個的！\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "什麼！？\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "怎麼了！？\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "......!\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "...이곳은...?\n그래. 난 구황회에 있지...\n...또 그런 꿈을 꾸는 건가...\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»빨리 감기»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Still", "노랫소리"], "content": ""}, {"id": 5, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Store", "문이 열린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "...잠이 안 와?\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "아, 깨웠나 보네?\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "아니, 아직 안 자고 있었어.\n목소리가 들리길래.\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "아으으... 진짜 춥다.... Node 03의 겨울은 상상 이상이야...\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "이곳의 기후는 Node 08처럼 완벽하게 복원되지 않아서 온도차가 꽤 큰 편이야. 창문 닫을까?\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "아니.\n야경을 좀 더 바라보고 싶어.\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "옷이라도 더 걸치던지. 감기 걸린다고. 자.\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "넌 안 입어?\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "방금 Nora와 같이 기계실에서 계속 장비 최적화 작업을 했거든. 아직도 더워 죽을 것 같아. 그러니까 너 입어.\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "또 납셨네~\n착한 남자인\"척\" 하는 Simon 씨?\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "그래그래... 멋대로 생각해.\n...방금 부른 거, 《Still》인가? 네 노랫소리를 듣는 것도 참으로 오랜만이로군.\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "...그냥 나오는대로 흥얼거렸을 뿐이야.\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\nDiego가 가족들을 위협할 수도 있을 거라고 관리국에 있는 친구에게 말해놨어. 그러니 너무 걱정할 필요 없을 거야.\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "예전에 말했던 Nate라는 사람?\n관리국에서 널 보내줬다는 그 사람이지?\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "맞아.\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "...그런데 왜 갑자기 이 얘기를?\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "네가 예전에 말했잖아. \n넌 불안해지면 그 노래를 부르곤 한다고.\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "난 괜찮아... 그냥 몇 가지 일이 조금 생각나서.\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": ".......\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "예전에 네게 사과했을 때... 참 두서없이 엉터리로 말했던 것 같은데.... 그래도... 계속 네게 사과하고 싶어. 역시 아직도 내 스스로가 용서가 안 되나 봐. 너는... 날 용서할 수 있어?\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "말했잖아? 너도 이제 그만 과거를 내려놔. 그렇지 않으면 앞으로 나아갈 수 없어. 너나 나나 그 일들에 대한 용서는 이제 더 이상 중요한 게 아니라고.\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "응... 맞는 말이야.\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "하암~~\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "네가 하품을 다하네? 희한한 일일세.\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "이틀 동안 한숨도 못 잤거든... \n지금은 진짜 자야 할 것 같아. 너도 일찍 자도록 해. 내일은 PAFF가 능력을 사용해서 단서를 찾아볼 예정이야. 그때 얻게 된 정보를 내게 보고해줘.\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "바람 조금만 더 쐬다 올게.\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "응. 그 재킷은 너 가져.\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "응? 됐어.\n어휴, 땀 냄새.\n도로 가져가.\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "정말? 내가 맡아보지... 괜찮은 것 같은데?\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "냄새난다고! 가져가, 가져가.\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "잠깐! 주머니 안에 뭐 들어있으니까 던지지는... 크윽!\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "아앗!\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Impact", "넘어진다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "....아파라...\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "image", "attrs": ["cpos2301"], "content": ""}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "..........\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "..........\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Move", "일어선다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": 